Package hms.entity.appointment

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
hms.entity.appointment.Appointment
public class Appointment extends Object
Represents an appointment with details such as patient ID, doctor ID, date, time, and appointment status.

    • Appointment

      public Appointment(String patientId, String doctorId, LocalDate date, LocalTime time)
      Constructs an appointment with the specified patient ID, doctor ID, date, and time. The appointment status is set to PENDING by default.
      Parameters:
      patientId - the ID of the patient.
      doctorId - the ID of the doctor.
      date - the date of the appointment.
      time - the time of the appointment.

    • Appointment

      Parameters:
      uuid - the unique identifier for the appointment.
      patientId - the ID of the patient.
      doctorId - the ID of the doctor.
      appointmentStatus - the status of the appointment.
      date - the date of the appointment.
      time - the time of the appointment.
